90  the EDMA transfers are implemented using blocking approach, (data path task
91  pending on semaphore, waiting for the transfer completion event, posted by
92  EDMA transfer completion intedrupt. In these cases since the EDMA transfers
93  are faster than DSP processing, polling approach is more appropriate. */
